The '''International Studies Conference (ISC)''' is an annual [[meeting|conference]] taking place since 2008 in [[Łódź]], [[Poland]] showing Polish students possibilities of studying abroad, especially in the United Kingdom and the United States. The conference each year gathers students, [[Alumnus|alumni]] and [[lecturer]]s from world-leading academic institutions including [[London School of Economics|The London School of Economics and Political Science]], [[University of Warwick]], [[University College London|UCL]], [[University of Oxford]] and [[Harvard University]].
